  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->Group<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function returns the name
  of the node group running the workunit. Not supported on Roxie clusters.
  This name is used in <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End --> code to specify the target <!-- DNT-Start -->CLUSTER<!-- DNT-End --> for an <!-- DNT-Start -->OUTPUT<!-- DNT-End -->
  action or a <!-- DNT-Start -->PERSISTed<!-- DNT-End --> attribute.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

